t.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:41:40.000Z","msg":"不能同意更多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a895d24f6c8e2ebb5b43c637f7bb671c1124739c","tid":830949,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:43:32.000Z","msg":"連登排行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb6e69d2310c01683b9043759fac5f3089de738","tid":830949,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T18:46:09.000Z","msg":"補充資料 1：<br />\n<br />\n大學教育資助委員會（<span style=\"color: blue;\">教資會</span>）University Grants Committee (<span style=\"color: blue;\">UGC</span>) 旗下有八間大學（<span style=\"color: blue;\">八大</span>）<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XvYe59\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXvYe59&h=1f0468e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VNvPLw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVNvPLw&h=63a58961&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當中本身<ins>一成立就已經係大學嘅大學</ins>只有 <span style=\"color: blue;\">HKUST 香港科技大學</span>，其餘七大院校論獲得／有「大學」頭銜嘅歷史倒時序如下：<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1881 年：<ins>官立師範學堂 Government Normal School</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1939 年：<ins>羅富國師範學院 Northcote Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/EvNTGR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEvNTGR&h=40e17823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1951 年：<ins>葛量洪師範學院 Grantham Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/ezdGkn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FezdGkn&h=c5fc7c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1960 年：<ins>柏立基師範學院 Sir Robert Black Training College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/RCcEyv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FRCcEyv&h=12ccbd6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1967 年：三所師範學院易名為<ins>教育學院 Colleges of Education</ins><br />\n<br />\n- 1974 年：<ins>香港工商師範學院 Hong Kong Technical Teachers' College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/VqcZuB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FVqcZuB&h=c0f18adb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1982 年：<ins>語文教育學院 Institute of Language in Education</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/FqDDTv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FFqDDTv&h=dc1fc511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1994 年：五所師訓學院合併為 <strong><ins>HKIEd 香港教育學院 (The Hong Kong Institute of Education)</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/nMVUzd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FnMVUzd&h=8b7ef130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2016 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">EdUHK 香港教育大學 (The Education University of Hong Kong)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/vCdavY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FvCdavY&h=ee4a3fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1888 年：<ins>格致書院</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1903 年：<ins>嶺南學堂</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- 1912 年：<ins>嶺南學校</ins>（廣州）<br />\n- <strong><ins>1927-1952 年</ins></strong>：<strong><ins>嶺南大學</ins></strong>（廣州）<br />\n- 1967 年：<ins>嶺南書院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/zgSkFR\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FzgSkFR&h=cf3d2753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- 1978 年：<ins>嶺南學院 Lingnan College</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jeNgV4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjeNgV4&h=2ebe6077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1999 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">LU 嶺南大學 (Lingnan University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/jyxiWg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FjyxiWg&h=10cb3cf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n<br />\n- 1937 年：<ins>香港官立高級工業學院</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/XzYfmH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXzYfmH&h=15df4cf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1947 年：<ins>香港工業專門學院 Hong Kong Technical College (HKTC)</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/mbJhbW\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmbJhbW&h=3831d4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/muYqzQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmuYqzQ&h=495bba67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 1972 年：<ins>香港理工學院 Hong Kong Polytechnic</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/MwMofP\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FMwMofP&h=3e6ef969&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://goo.gl/Z9za5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FZ9za5V&h=c7ce1665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1994 年</span></span>：獲頒授自我評審資格，取得大學地位，正名為 <span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">PolyU 香港理工大學 (The Hong Kong Polytechnic University)</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/fKwYmk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfKwYmk&h=6262f338&s={SI